rows.label: qst202406_0010
rows.name:
Ohh, nononononono! Terrible news! Tirkin
launch attack on us!

rows.label: qst202406_0020
rows.name: The Tirkin?!

rows.label: qst202406_0030
rows.name: Are they even capable of organizing an attack?!

rows.label: qst202406_0040
rows.name:
We get shipment on deck, giant box.
Then all of sudden, Tirkin leap out!

rows.label: qst202406_0050
rows.name: It completely unheard of! Whole of Goldmund in total uproar!

rows.label: qst202406_0060
rows.name: Hey! Hey, Nora. What do you think might be for dinner?

rows.label: qst202406_0070
rows.name: Nora not know. Tora not know either!

rows.label: qst202406_0080
rows.name: I'm really in something like a Stuffed Meaty Carrot mood.

rows.label: qst202406_0090
rows.name: Ah, so tasty...

rows.label: qst202406_0100
rows.name:
Yeah! Sometimes I dream about being
buried in a pile of Stuffed Meaty Carrots.

rows.label: qst202406_0110
rows.name:
Please focus, you two.
We do not have time for this inanity!

rows.label: qst202406_0120
rows.name: This very serious situation!

rows.label: qst202406_0130
rows.name:
If Tirkin go wild in Goldmund, business
in deep deep trouble!

rows.label: qst202406_0140
rows.name: This no time to be thinking about that!

rows.label: qst202406_0150
rows.name:
It extremely dangerous to stay here.
Must evacuate immediately!

rows.label: qst202406_0160
rows.name: Fool of a pon!

rows.label: qst202406_0170
rows.name:
Merchant without shop is like fish without water.
Noganga not move one inch!

rows.label: qst202406_0180
rows.name:
This all happen because you too weak and you
not shooshoo Tirkin!

rows.label: qst202406_0190
rows.name: It all your fault!

rows.label: qst202406_0200
rows.name:
Think of victims and lost revenue!
Noganga expect Drivers to clean up own mess!

rows.label: qst202406_0210
rows.name: It seems we've no choice but to step in.

rows.label: qst202406_0220
rows.name: Tirkin surely here to take revenge on you!

rows.label: qst202406_0230
rows.name:
Especially birdbrain! Birdbrain need to take
responsibility!

rows.label: qst202406_0240
rows.name: Huh? Do I really?

rows.label: qst202406_0250
rows.name:
But I don't even remember what I did...
I...guess it could've been our fault?

rows.label: qst202406_0260
rows.name: Whoa whoa whoa. Don't let 'em pin this on us.

rows.label: qst202406_0270
rows.name:
Anyway, this is no time for chitchat.
We've gotta minimize the casualties!

rows.label: qst202406_0280
rows.name: Come on, let's move, people!

rows.label: qst202406_0290
rows.name: That what Noganga like to see!

rows.label: qst202406_0300
rows.name:
Come on, Ibuki. We need to clear out the Tirkin
and save everyone on the ship!

rows.label: qst202406_0310
rows.name:
Jeez, do we have to? I feel like we're just
being roped into this...
